snippet.title: Cassette Beasts - Gameplay Trailer | ID@Xbox April 2023
snippet.description: This turn-based RPG with an 80's vibe lets you record monsters on to your cassette player to use in battle. Cassette Beasts comes to PC and Xbox Game Pass soon.
